review_text: Nice park with lots of benches and tables to sit and eat. Play parks for kids, skate park and a dog park as well. Lot of trees for shade. Not much grass sitting space though.

A great park for young families.
It features 2 large structures with slides and climbing walls for different ages. Multiple swings and a parent-baby swing too. There is also a storage space that contains rackets and balls that can be borrowed.

There is also a large water park.

This is beside a basketball court and a dog park.

This is a great dog park.  There's lots of space to play with my dog.   The fences are very high.  There are several benches and picnic tables to sit at

Beware - in wet weather, the park gets extremely muddy.

(Translated by Google) Excellent park with perfect water games for children, swing, banquet grounds, skate park and dog park. Convenience stores nearby and a Lafleur restaurant. If I only give 3 stars, it is because the space with the water games for children is really not cleaned enough and therefore becomes extremely slippery and therefore dangerous. Brown moss covers the ground in some places and many children (and adults) fall. It is really better to go there at the start of the season, June to mid July, then it's too dangerous and I don't want my child to open his head on the concrete.

(Original)
Excellent parc avec des jeux d'eau parfait pour les enfants, balançoire, terrains de banquet, skate park et parc à chien. Des dépanneurs tous proche et un restaurant Lafleur. Si je ne mets que 3 étoiles, c'est que l'espace avec les jeux d'eau pour les enfants n'est vraiment pas assez nettoyagé et devient donc extrêmement glissant et donc dangereux. De la mousse marron recouvre le sol à certains endroits et beaucoup d'enfants (et d'adultes) tombent. Il faut vraiment mieux y aller en début de saison, juin à mi juillet, ensuite c'est trop dangereux et je ne veux pas que mon enfant s'ouvre la tête sur le béton.
